title: #131 - Ninja And The End Of Twitch
description: On this episode of the H3 podcast we discuss Ninja's shocking announcement that he will no longer be streaming on twitch.tv, the Fortnite world cup, Saudi Arabia's plans for an artificial moon, alligator mukbang, the green goblin in the French military, Ethan's beef with Lil Tracy, and a whoooooooole lot more!
